-- Dabur India Plants to Raise as Much as 20 Billion Rupees for Acquisitions
-- Saikat Chatterjee
-- 2010-07-30T03:19:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-30/dabur-india-plants-to-raise-as-much-as-20-billion-rupees-for-acquisitions.html

          
          
             Dabur India Ltd. may raise as much
as 20 billion rupees to fund acquisitions, Spokesman Byas Anand
said in a telephone interview. The company’s board has passed an
“enabling resolution” to raise the money, he said.  
